text: Adrián Andres Puentes Peréz is an archer from Cuba. He was born on 3 July 1988. Puentes competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics.Adrián Andrés PuentesAdrian Andres PUENTES PEREZ == References == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban archers Category:Olympians for Cuba
